articles.author: Chris Isidore, Vanessa Yurkevich
articles.title: UAW reaches tentative agreement with Stellantis, expands strike at GM - CNN
articles.description: The UAW has reached a tentative agreement with Stellantis, which makes vehicles under the Dodge, Ram, Chrysler and Jeep brands.
articles.content: The United Auto Workers unioncame to a tenative agreement with Stellantis Saturday. But it expanded the strike against General Motors, Americas largest automaker and the last remaining Big Three holdâ€¦ [+8575 chars]
